{"tid":1907670,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有咁既另一半 無論如何都唔好放手","createTime":"2020-03-02T18:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T20:13:39.000Z","uid":132434,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3891478f88cc4ab7d39c14eba7eaafb4582f513b","tid":1907670,"uid":132434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:26:38.000Z","msg":"本身另一半有離開香港 <br />\n喺另一個國家發展既機會<br />\n為咗我選擇留低<br />\n因為我一句說話 戒咗煙<br />\n唔會順口開河<br />\n應承咗帶我去見屋企人<br />\n佢真係會主動安排我參加聚會<br />\n手機成個相簿 幾乎得我既相/同我既合照<br />\n除咗我 唔比人喺佢嫁車同房度食嘢<br />\n自知份人硬頸 但你都會盡你所能安慰我<br />\n盡量冷靜去傾 睇吓有咩解決方法<br />\n好多時都好就我 仲話中意喺我面前認輸<br />\n即使曾經佢身邊既人 有質疑過我<br />\n依然無條件信任 維護我<br />\n多謝你男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有好多不足 但我會努力去改 同維繫<br />\n你包容我既程度大到<br />\n對住你有時真係發唔到脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n情侶相處到 溝通好 政見一樣 仲要一齊喺各方面進步既真係唔容易<br />\n希望搵到個夾既黃絲做另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6bd5ba1a5d66152d5133cd7509160a4cf4512a","tid":1907670,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:40:27.000Z","msg":"放咗"},{"pid":"6d565bb38677aef9f96bb19fc7bc7950e92689b3","tid":1907670,"uid":73804,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"得得得 知你好幸福"},{"pid":"6da03550fda6210ef19a4f8c4dd40adb6687dae3","tid":1907670,"uid":57237,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:47:19.000Z","msg":"關人撚事咩"},{"pid":"bd2b4186a0fffb2a70af6fdcfe4c1b9dba18118a","tid":1907670,"uid":3935,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:49:56.000Z","msg":"Welcome to facebook"},{"pid":"6ea50145ceb3b75d0ae1254a7a4a6e1cdde5f9d2","tid":1907670,"uid":59955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci